strings:
<voice_0x01000D40><se_low>Yangus: I need to speak wiv Red.
Yer gonna 'ave to let us through.
<voice_0x01000D41><se_low>*: Yangus! You think Red's gonna wanna see your ugly mush!? Get out of 'ere! Hop it!

<voice_0x01000D42><se_low>Yangus: Don't you boss me around, mate!
I ain't goin' nowhere 'til I see Red.
So shift, skivvy!

<voice_0x01000D43><se_low>*: Skivvy!?
Who the 'ell d'you think you are!?

<voice_0x01000D44><se_high>Red: What's all the noise!?
I can hear your gabbin' from in here!

<voice_0x01000D45><se_low>*: S-Sorry, boss!
I got some geezer wiv no manners out 'ere.
He'll be gone in a mo...

<voice_0x01000D46><se_high>Red: It's Yangus, isn't it?
Just let him in.
I'll speak to him meself.

<voice_0x01000D47><se_low>*: ...You 'eard the boss!
Go on! Inside wiv ya!
